I"º<h3 id="how-to-accept-eula-when-yum-installing-something">How to accept EULA when yum installing something?</h3>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>- name: Install mssql-tools and msodbcsql
  yum:
    name: ""
    state: present
  with_items:
    - mssql-tools
    - msodbcsql
  environment:
    ACCEPT_EULA: 'y'
  become: true
  become_user: root
</code></pre></div></div>
